modules.description: This module defines a comprehensive set of icon constants representing UI elements and actions, along with operations to convert them to S-expressions, retrieve frame indices, generate SVG nodes with customizable attributes, and access their string names. It works primarily with the enumerated type `t` listing each icon variant, and supports integration with UI rendering through functions like `svg` that produce virtual DOM nodes. Concrete use cases include rendering icons in a web-based code editor interface, distinguishing file types, representing version control actions, and enhancing UI components with visual indicators.
